ComicInfo.Summary: A NEW THREAT EMERGES! While the team recuperates from its confrontation with Simon Cox, a world power tests the waters of biological warfare. Lark, Alexis and DJ all return home to heal and to refine their training. With their powers becoming increasingly dangerous, as well as their new roles as living weapons, all of this forces them to evaluate just who and what they have become. Meanwhile, China has been secretly developing bio-weapons. Now they are ready to field-test them as well as their "super-soldiers". Guest cover by ANDY PARK!!
